是啊
Yeah.

522
01:01:25,960 --> 01:01:29,120
你还记得我一直说的那棵树吗
And you know that tree I'm always going on about?

523
01:01:29,120 --> 01:01:30,580
记得
Yeah.

524
01:01:30,780 --> 01:01:34,440
这药是拿那种树做的
Well, this drug is made from trees like that.

525
01:01:34,510 --> 01:01:35,930
- 是吗 - 没错
- It is? - Yeah.

526
01:01:36,100 --> 01:01:37,460
真的?
Seriously?

527
01:01:37,660 --> 01:01:40,810
一直以来 我们本能出去砍掉它
All this time we could have gone out there and just chopped it down.

528
01:01:42,190 --> 01:01:43,850
但那一棵不行
But not that one.

529
01:01:48,170 --> 01:01:50,390
那一棵是我们的朋友
That one's our friend.

530
01:02:28,510 --> 01:02:30,160
你在哪
Where are you?

531
01:02:31,170 --> 01:02:32,530
我在这
I'm here.

532
01:02:34,950 --> 01:02:37,710
你能让我妈妈好转吗
Can you do it? Can you make my mum better?

533
01:02:37,720 --> 01:02:40,880
你母亲能被治愈的话 紫杉树会那么做
If your mother can be healed, the yew tree will do it.

534
01:02:43,720 --> 01:02:48,050
- 所以是可以咯? - 你还是不知道你为什么召唤我
- So that's a yes? - You still don't know why you called me.

535
01:02:48,050 --> 01:02:51,800
我没有召唤你 就算有也是为了我妈妈
I didn't call you. And even if I did, it was obviously for mum.

536
01:02:51,800 --> 01:02:53,270
- 是吗 - 还能怎么样
- Was it? - What else?

537
01:02:53,280 --> 01:02:55,780
那些蠢故事毫无意义
To listen to idiotic stories that make no sense.

538
01:02:55,790 --> 01:03:00,840
现在还不是讲第三个故事的时候 但快了 在那之后
It is not yet time for the third tale. But soon. And after that...

539
01:03:00,840 --> 01:03:03,640
你要告诉我你的故事 康纳·奥马利
you will tell me your story, Conor O'Malley.

540
01:03:03,640 --> 01:03:06,080
不
No.

541
01:03:06,250 --> 01:03:09,420
不 不是这个 这只是一场噩梦
No, not this. That's just a nightmare.

542
01:03:09,590 --> 01:03:12,050
别这样
No, please.

543
01:03:15,250 --> 01:03:18,600
那不是真的 那不过是一场噩梦
That's not my truth. That's just a nightmare.

544
01:03:18,770 --> 01:03:21,940
然而这会在第三个故事之后发生
Nevertheless, this will happen after the third tale.

545
01:03:22,110 --> 01:03:24,310
我想知道我妈妈会怎么样
I want to know what's going to happen with my mum.

546
01:03:25,340 --> 01:03:28,260
别浪费你被给予的宝贵时间
Do not waste the precious time that is given you.

547
01:03:28,260 --> 01:03:31,250
等等 你要去哪
Wait. Where are you going?

548
01:03:31,410 --> 01:03:34,050
如果你是治愈之树 那我需要你去救治
If you are a tree of healing, then I need you to heal.

549
01:03:35,920 --> 01:03:38,130
我会的
And so I shall.

550
01:04:08,270 --> 01:04:13,520
康纳 我会回来的 我保证 你来洛杉矶过圣诞
Conor, I'll come back. I promise, alright. And you'll come to LA for Christmas.

551
01:04:13,590 --> 01:04:16,090
我不想圣诞就留妈妈一个人
I wont leave mum alone for Christmas.

552
01:04:16,150 --> 01:04:19,530
- 康纳你妈妈用的这个药... - 会让她好转
- Conor this medicine your mum's taking... - Is going to make her well.

553
01:04:19,540 --> 01:04:21,590
康纳 很可能不会
No, Conor, it probably isn't.

554
01:04:21,590 --> 01:04:23,790
- 会的 - 这是最后一博了 儿子
- Yes it is. - No, it's a last stage effort, son.

555
01:04:23,950 --> 01:04:26,370
会治愈她的 我知道的
It will heal her. I know it.

556
01:04:27,400 --> 01:04:29,650
这就是它来的原因 一定是的
It is the reason it came. It has to be.

557
01:04:29,650 --> 01:04:32,400
- 什么来的原因 - 怪物
- Reason what came? - The monster.

558
01:04:32,400 --> 01:04:34,490
- 康纳  什么  - 它总会12点07分出现
- Conor, what? - It comes to 12h07.

559
01:04:34,500 --> 01:04:37,040
起初我以为这是一个梦 但它不是
At first I thought it was a dream, but there is always...

560
01:04:37,210 --> 01:04:38,770
康纳 别说了 那是个梦
Stop. It is a dream.

561
01:04:38,940 --> 01:04:41,260
只是个梦 我很抱歉你得面对这件事
That's all it is. I'm sorry you have to face this...

562
01:04:41,310 --> 01:04:43,580
但你得勇敢起来
but you have to be brave.

563
01:04:44,280 --> 01:04:47,030
明白吗
Do you understand?

564
01:04:47,970 --> 01:04:49,670
来吧
Come on.

565
01:04:50,690 --> 01:04:52,090
来吧
Come on.

566
01:05:02,360 --> 01:05:04,480
我会尽快回来
I'll be back as soon as I can.

567
01:05:04,930 --> 01:05:07,580
如果不够快怎么办
What if it's not fast enough?

568
01:05:13,070 --> 01:05:14,160
康纳 听着
Conor, listen...

569
01:05:14,330 --> 01:05:17,630
- 没事的 - 什么没事的
- It's okay. - What is okay?

570
01:05:17,790 --> 01:05:19,250
只是...
Just...

571
01:05:19,250 --> 01:05:21,440
你不用尽快
You don't have to.

572
01:06:29,550 --> 01:06:32,140
看到没
Look. Do you see it?

573
01:06:32,300 --> 01:06:34,140
看到了吗 你能挥手吗
Do you see it? Can you wave?

574
01:06:34,300 --> 01:06:37,150
你能看到他吗
Can you see him?

575
01:06:37,310 --> 01:06:41,740
向外婆挥手
And then we wave to grandma.

576
01:06:45,160 --> 01:06:46,990
嗨 外婆
Hello grandma.

577
01:06:47,160 --> 01:06:49,410
康 向外婆和妈妈打招呼
Con, you can say hello to grandma and mum?

578
01:06:49,580 --> 01:06:51,750
嗨 外婆
Hello Grandma.

579
01:06:51,920 --> 01:06:54,170
这就对了
Here we go.

580
01:06:54,340 --> 01:06:57,180
妈妈已经听过这个很多次了
Mum has heard this many times.

581
01:06:57,240 --> 01:06:59,080
你准备好了吗
Are you ready?

582
01:06:59,240 --> 01:07:01,420
康 过来
Con, come sit here.

583
01:07:01,580 --> 01:07:04,250
康 看啊
Con, look.

584
01:07:04,420 --> 01:07:07,090
- 你好 外婆  - 妈妈...
- Hello grandma. - Mama...

585
01:07:07,260 --> 01:07:09,260
妈妈
- one... - Mama.

586
01:07:09,430 --> 01:07:11,710
很好
There we go.

587
01:07:11,710 --> 01:07:14,350
外婆 我们在画画
We are doing your picture, grandma.

588
01:07:14,520 --> 01:07:17,360
然后混在一起
And then mix it together.

589
01:07:17,530 --> 01:07:19,030
这是什么颜色
What color is that?

590
01:07:19,600 --> 01:07:20,930
棕色
Brown.

591
01:07:23,540 --> 01:07:25,370
- 好看又幸运的棕色 - 棕色
- It is a nice lodgy brown. - Brown.

592
01:07:25,540 --> 01:07:28,380
- 但这里有棕色了 - 没错
- But we have brown here. - That's true.

593
01:07:28,540 --> 01:07:31,840
看到了吗
What can you see?

594
01:07:32,010 --> 01:07:35,010
那是什么 它们是什么
What is that? What are those?

595
01:07:35,180 --> 01:07:37,180
你觉得这些是什么
What do you... What are these?

596
01:07:37,350 --> 01:07:40,400
- 眼睛 - 眼睛 没错
- Eyes. - Eyes. That's it.

597
01:07:40,560 --> 01:07:43,150
生活永远都在眼睛之中
Life is always in the eyes.

598
01:07:43,670 --> 01:07:46,240
如果你懂的话
If you get that...

599
01:07:46,240 --> 01:07:48,820
你会是个出色的艺术家
you will be a proper artist.

600
01:07:49,270 --> 01:07:51,150
很好
Yes.

601
01:07:51,540 --> 01:07:54,290
看啊
Look.

602
01:07:54,460 --> 01:07:56,300
就是这么画眼睛
This is how we draw the eyes in...

603
01:07:56,470 --> 01:08:00,540
这里是眼睛捕捉映像的地方
because this is where the eyes catch the reflection.

604
01:08:01,600 --> 01:08:05,440
在眼睛里 我们能看到生活 看见没
There we see the life in the eyes. See that?

605
01:08:05,600 --> 01:08:10,320
再来一次 这就是生活
Do it again. It's life.

606
01:08:13,320 --> 01:08:16,750
用铅笔吧
Maybe if we take a pencil...

607
01:08:16,910 --> 01:08:20,590
然后在那里画
and you can draw on that...

608
01:08:20,750 --> 01:08:23,010
想试试吗
Do you want to try it?

609
01:08:23,170 --> 01:08:25,390
让我看看
Show me how you do it.

610
01:08:37,660 --> 01:08:41,250
看 康
Look, Con.

611
01:08:41,410 --> 01:08:46,420
那是他的头发 这是他的眉毛
That's his hair and this is his eyebrow.

612
01:08:47,880 --> 01:08:50,550
这边是眼睛
There's the eyes.

613
01:08:50,720 --> 01:08:53,470
看 这是他的嘴
Oh look, there's his mouth.

614
01:08:53,640 --> 01:08:57,310
这是他的嘴 他非得愤怒
There's his mouth. He is very angry.

615
01:08:57,480 --> 01:08:59,650
看到了吗
Can you see?

616
01:08:59,820 --> 01:09:02,400
看啊
Look at that.

617
01:09:02,970 --> 01:09:07,190
然后我们画张脸
And then we start to make a face.

618
01:09:07,190 --> 01:09:09,250
然后
And then...

619
01:09:09,410 --> 01:09:11,670
这就是我们的怪物
there's our monster.

620
01:09:11,830 --> 01:09:13,420
这就是怪物
There's the monster.

621
01:09:13,590 --> 01:09:16,180
看这怪物
Look at the monster.

622
01:09:50,600 --> 01:09:52,610
慢点
Very slowly.

623
01:09:54,190 --> 01:09:56,200
就是这样
That's it.

624
01:09:59,870 --> 01:10:02,120
没错 好的
That's it, okay.

625
01:10:13,190 --> 01:10:15,650
今早是30分钟的考试
Okay, so 30 minutes exam this morning...

626
01:10:15,810 --> 01:10:19,650
考的是过去两周我们都做过的东西
and this is all the stuff we've been doing for the last two weeks.

627
01:10:19,820 --> 01:10:24,290
复习过就不会有意外
So if you've done your revision, there will be no surprises.

628
01:10:28,830 --> 01:10:32,100
你们马上就得合上书本
So in a moment I'm going to ask you to turn your pages over.

629
01:10:32,100 --> 01:10:38,180
下面30分钟都不准说话 要保持完全安静
There will be no talking for the next 30 minutes. I want total silence...

630
01:10:38,180 --> 01:10:42,480
因为你们要用的是大脑而不是嘴
because you are going to use your brains, not your mouths.

631
01:10:42,650 --> 01:10:44,900
30分钟...
So 30 minutes...

632
01:10:45,070 --> 01:10:47,740
现在开始 祝你们好运
Starting now. Good luck.

633
01:11:14,480 --> 01:11:17,940
在这么久之后
I think I've finally figures you out.

634
01:11:18,010 --> 01:11:20,510
我想我总算搞懂你了
After all this time.

635
01:11:20,680 --> 01:11:25,100
你只是想让人对你印象深刻
All you're looking for is someone kick your head in.

636
01:11:25,270 --> 01:11:26,770
但你知道吗
But you know what?

637
01:11:26,940 --> 01:11:29,940
我不再是那个家伙了
I'm not that guy anymore.

638
01:11:36,010 --> 01:11:38,130
再见 奥马利
Goodbye, O'Malley.

639
01:11:38,160 --> 01:11:40,920
我再也不会看见你
I no longer see you.

640
01:11:41,080 --> 01:11:44,250
现在你对我来说是隐形的
Now you're invisible to me too.

641
01:11:45,210 --> 01:11:47,610
希望你妈妈会好起来
I hope your mum gets better.

642
01:12:12,360 --> 01:12:14,390
你怎么这么慢
What took you so long?

643
01:12:14,390 --> 01:12:17,710
是时候讲第三个故事了
It's time for the third tale.

644
01:12:20,510 --> 01:12:23,840
曾经有个隐形人
There was once an invisible man...

645
01:12:23,840 --> 01:12:27,020
厌倦了不被人看见
who was grown tired of being unseen.

646
01:12:27,190 --> 01:12:30,990
实际上 他不是隐形的
It was not that he was actually invisible.

647
01:12:32,780 --> 01:12:36,450
只是人们习惯于无视他
It was just the people had become used to not seeing him.

648
01:12:36,620 --> 01:12:41,460
有一天 隐形人再也受不了了
One day, the invisible man couldn't stand it anymore.

649
01:12:41,620 --> 01:12:46,380
他好奇如果没人看见你
He kept wondering, if no one sees you...

650
01:12:46,550 --> 01:12:50,050
那你真的存在吗
Are you really there at all?

651
01:12:50,220 --> 01:12:53,060
隐形人做了什么
What did the invisible man do?

652
01:12:53,580 --> 01:12:57,660
他召唤了怪物
He called for a monster.

653
01:13:15,710 --> 01:13:18,820
我都不知道跟你说什么好 奥马利
I don't even know what to say to you, O'Malley.

654
01:13:20,090 --> 01:13:23,930
你把他送进了医院
You sent him to hospital.

655
01:13:24,100 --> 01:13:26,850
他父母威胁要起诉
His parents are threatening to sue.

656
01:13:27,020 --> 01:13:30,070
- 那不是我 - 什么
- It wasn't me. - What was that?

657
01:13:30,070 --> 01:13:32,530
那不是我
Wasn't me.

658
01:13:35,530 --> 01:13:39,000
我不是隐形的
I'm not invisible. I'm not invisible.

659
01:13:39,060 --> 01:13:41,810
如果你想被人注意 奥马利 那可不是最好的办法
If you want to be seen, O'Malley, this is not the best way.

660
01:13:41,810 --> 01:13:46,550
我不是隐形的 你听见了吗
I'm not invisible. Did you hear me? I'm not invisible.

661
01:13:46,710 --> 01:13:51,400
根据学校规定 你会被立即开除
School rules dictate immediately exclusion.

662
01:13:52,970 --> 01:13:57,810
但我是一名教师 我怎么可能做得到
But how could I do that and consider myself any kind of a teacher?

663
01:13:58,810 --> 01:14:00,530
回去上课吧
Go back to class.

664
01:14:00,530 --> 01:14:04,860
我们改日再谈 今天就不谈了
We will talk about this one day, but not today.

665
01:14:05,400 --> 01:14:08,740
你不惩罚我?
You're not punishing me?

666
01:14:08,910 --> 01:14:12,330
这有什么意义
What could possibly be the point?

667
01:14:25,100 --> 01:14:27,690
我来给你们举个健康情绪的例子
Well, let me give you an example of emotional wellness.

668
01:14:27,850 --> 01:14:31,090
你们知道有时说不是有多困难 对吗
You know how difficult it is sometimes to say no. Right?

669
01:14:31,590 --> 01:14:37,620
而当你们终于有勇气说出口时 感觉会很棒 这是为什么呢
And how good it feels when you finally find the courage to say it anyway. Why is that?

670
01:14:38,340 --> 01:14:40,330
你有空吗
Do you have a moment?

671
01:14:43,500 --> 01:14:45,170
怎么了
Hoi, wat is is?

672
01:14:45,330 --> 01:14:47,840
我们刚接到医院电话
We just got a call from the hospital.

673
01:14:48,010 --> 01:14:53,050
恐怕康纳的母亲快不行了 他们想要他过去
I am afraid that Conor's mother is not going to make it. They want him to come there.

674
01:15:22,200 --> 01:15:24,440
你不一起吗
Aren't you coming?

675
01:15:25,500 --> 01:15:27,670
我就待在这
I'll be right here.

676
01:16:01,010 --> 01:16:03,620
你的手怎么了
What did you do to your hands?

677
01:16:09,620 --> 01:16:12,450
是要谈话 对吗
It's the talk isn't it?

678
01:16:12,620 --> 01:16:15,830
最近每个人都想谈话
Everybody wants to have a talk lately.

679
01:16:20,120 --> 01:16:21,670
康
Con...

680
01:16:22,700 --> 01:16:23,910
看着我
Look at me.

681
01:16:28,370 --> 01:16:31,420
今早我跟医生谈过话
I spoke to the doctor this morning.

682
01:16:37,470 --> 01:16:40,650
新的治疗方式没作用
The new treatment it's... it's not working.

683
01:16:41,660 --> 01:16:44,580
紫杉树的那个?
The one from the yew tree?

684
01:16:47,310 --> 01:16:48,560
是的
Yeah.

685
01:16:49,830 --> 01:16:52,030
怎么会没作用
How can it not be working?

686
01:16:52,090 --> 01:16:56,310
一切都发生太快 超出了他们的预想
Things just happen fast. Faster than they thought.

687
01:16:56,470 --> 01:16:59,730
- 怎么会没作用呢 - 不知道
- How can it not be working? - I don't know.

688
01:16:59,890 --> 01:17:02,020
它必须要有作用
It has to.

689
01:17:07,360 --> 01:17:11,530
那现在怎么说 下一步怎么治疗
So what happens now? What's going to be the next treatment?

690
01:17:17,290 --> 01:17:19,790
我很抱歉
I'm so sorry.

691
01:17:21,270 --> 01:17:26,510
我一生中从没这么抱歉过
I've never been more sorry about anything in my life.

692
01:17:36,910 --> 01:17:39,300
你生气的话 也没事 康
It's okay that you're angry, Con.

693
01:17:40,530 --> 01:17:42,390
真的
It really is.

694
01:17:43,790 --> 01:17:47,760
我也很气自己告诉你真相
I'm pretty angry too, to tell you the truth.

695
01:17:49,390 --> 01:17:51,340
但是 康纳...
But Con...

696
01:17:56,080 --> 01:17:58,450
康纳 你在听吗
Con, are you listening?

697
01:18:01,770 --> 01:18:03,960
有一天...
One day...

698
01:18:05,400 --> 01:18:09,610
如果你回想这件事 为自己的生气而感到难过
if you look back and you feel bad for being so angry...

699
01:18:09,610 --> 01:18:15,470
你甚至可以向我倾诉 但你必须清楚 这没关系
you couldn't even speak to me, you have to know that was okay...

700
01:18:21,880 --> 01:18:24,720
我就知道你会难过
That I knew.

701
01:18:27,170 --> 01:18:33,480
因为你要对我说的 不用你说出口 我就已经知道了
Because I know everything you need to tell me without you having to say it out loud.

702
01:18:37,900 --> 01:18:41,070
如果你要摔东西
And if you need to break things...

703
01:18:42,870 --> 01:18:45,760
那就去摔吧
By God you break them.

704
01:18:46,290 --> 01:18:49,270
使劲摔
Break them good and hard.

705
01:18:49,280 --> 01:18:52,670
我会伴你左右 康
And I'll be right there, Con.

706
01:19:03,810 --> 01:19:07,050
我希望我能有100年
